response.overview: "AKA" is a thrilling and emotionally charged film that will have audiences on the edge of their seats. The movie follows a tough-as-nails special ops agent who is tasked with infiltrating a dangerous crime syndicate. As he delves deeper into the organization, he finds his morality and beliefs tested like never before.
